high_descs: Round, go straight, then turn left to go to the counter above the trash bin.
Pick up the plate with the spatula on it, on the counter.
Turn left, then go straight, then turn right to face the sink.
Put the plate in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a plate with a spatula on it in the sink.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the wall, then turn left to the counter.
Pick up the pan with the spatula in it from the counter.
Turn left and walk to the sink.
Put the pan and the spatula in the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the pan and spatula in the sink.

high_descs: Move across the room to the far right side of the wood counter top
Pick up the frying pan on the counter with the spatula in it
Carry the frying pan over to the sink basin
Place the frying pan and the spatula inside of the sink
anns.task_desc: Move a pan and spatula to the sink
